text.section:
The petition shall be presented in the form of a resolution passed by the city legislative body and shall contain:
An accurate map of the city;
An affidavit certifying new growth of the city that may be through any of the following:
Annexation since the most recent federal decennial census;
Property valuation records;
Population counts conducted by the city, or by a person contracted with the city;
Census estimates of the United States Bureau of Census; and
Any other data that the city may provide to certify the additional growth of the city since the most recent federal decennial census.
